Yves Saint Laurent Elle Eau de Parfum - 90 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.4500

Sensual lively witty chic and completely unpredictable - revel in the myriad shades that make you a truly unique woman. A luxury scent that embodies modern classic Yves Saint Laurent Elle tantalizes and teases your senses. Created by renowned perfumers Jacques Cavalier and Olivier Cresp this beautiful Eau De Parfum is made for the iconic house of Yves Saint Laurent.

With each ingredient hand-picked to enhance every feminine nuance this perfume celebrates the vibrant diverse and bewildering spirit of a woman. Notes of tropical sweet lychee entangles with fresh floral notes of peony for the free-spirited daredevil who still cries while watching her favourite movie. Bubbly yet sharp witted the peppy and vivacious hints of pink berry that cuts across the mint-woody undertone of patchouli suits her. Her exhilarating passion makes way for a mature and supportive quality just like the refreshingly peppery freesia gives way to the warming scent of cedarwood. A garden of natural extracts blend together to create this floral woody fragrance that leaves you feeling like an ethereal nymph. This perfume is encased in a slender rectangular ampoule that strikes the perfect balance between class and flamboyance. Painted a delicious shade of fuchsia along with gold accents the YSL name is proudly emblazoned on the surface of this flacon. For every mood and every occasion all you need is a spritz of Elle.

This is a subversive perfume of its time but with festive chypre notes that emulate the joie de vivre of a glass of champagne fun flighty but elegant. The middle notes come from the flowery notes of Rose Otto and precede the richness and quality of woody notes with Nectarine - Rose Otto - Oakmoss.
